{"tid":901731,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果讀到中四 中文都仲好差 有無得救","createTime":"2018-11-14T08:57:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T14:45:16.000Z","uid":33381,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"2dec61f2e407a60ea5eb666f1b5af46eda586a34","tid":901731,"uid":33381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:57:13.000Z","msg":"有個補習學生 讀緊中四 英文幾好<br />\n但偏偏中文個底就差得緊要<br />\n補咗成年 都依然無乜進步<br />\n平時唔會睇書唔會睇報紙<br />\n一啲長少少嘅文都唔會睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話一睇就眼瞓...<br />\n<br />\n閱讀理解唔明作者想講咩 <br />\n教咗好多次都唔識答題 唔識組織<br />\n作文有時我會唔明佢寫緊咩<br />\n好多字唔識寫 <br />\n成語又唔識多隻<br />\n更加唔好話嗰啲拋書包嘢<br />\n<br />\n我平時都係同佢一齊讀嗰12篇範文 <br />\n叫佢做下閱讀理解同作文<br />\n佢最近測驗得10幾分....<br />\n問佢咩事佢話唔識做瞓咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喂大佬呀你鳩寫啲博下都好呀<br />\n好灰 唔知點可以幫佢<br />\n有衝動印啲中一中二 甚至小六嘅作業俾佢打底<br />\n你地覺得佢仲有無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7e07657cf7f0bf45fd69c91ee47a8aa251615b","tid":901731,"uid":71508,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:59:56.000Z","msg":"正常"},{"pid":"1484e9be4420eccaefe8d9a3e3b36b9c19d39cf2","tid":901731,"uid":7458,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:00:36.000Z","msg":"如果佢本身冇心機學中文<br />\n點幫都救唔返<br />\n<br />\n我以前都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc009c31c61bbfe49f6ad8b31d9cff574b44ad56","tid":901731,"uid":208817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:01:52.000Z","msg":"叫佢認真讀書好過幫佢補中文底"},{"pid":"dae94426cc76ee91fd14915320097648b730c22d","tid":901731,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:04:06.000Z","msg":"試下比啲好撚好睇嘅文佢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4900ec9e1df21fce149671868e4a0695a71043ad","tid":901731,"uid":33381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1484e9be4420eccaefe8d9a3e3b36b9c19d39cf2","tid":901731,"uid":7458,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:00:36.000Z","msg":"如果佢本身冇心機學中文<br />\n點幫都救唔返<br />\n<br />\n我以前都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:15:02.000Z","msg":"你而家中文都好差?<br />\n佢係差到我覺得佢上連登都好難表達自己要講咩<br />\n不過佢的確完全無心機學中文<br />\n無心機學搞到個底差 越差又越無心機學..."},{"pid":"bc2bb162f96ab7869d6412cdbc1889be241b2414","tid":901731,"uid":33381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc009c31c61bbfe49f6ad8b31d9cff574b44ad56","tid":901731,"uid":208817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:01:52.000Z","msg":"叫佢認真讀書好過幫佢補中文底"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:16:03.000Z","msg":"咁佢都算認真 俾佢啲嘢又會做 <br />\nFeel到佢係盡咗力<br />\n但都真係好差"},{"pid":"bfb328f06e6aa1c6c851fafd2d769f1140d72b7d","tid":901731,"uid":27030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:18:21.000Z","msg":"平時講中文說話能力有冇問題先<br />\n如果冇問題應該重可以由說話開始train"},{"pid":"76cabf71bf7edf56d1d987b4b6e942ee85167c3a","tid":901731,"uid":33381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dae94426cc76ee91fd14915320097648b730c22d","tid":901731,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:04:06.000Z","msg":"試下比啲好撚好睇嘅文佢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:19:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無好推介...<br />\n電影劇集佢都麻麻<br />\n古裝戲佢又唔睇 愛情又唔like<br />\n佢話佢鍾意睇音樂劇之類?例如lala land<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3c1872b169716fb8cffdeeb439aad9da548d0a","tid":901731,"uid":221857,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:19:43.000Z","msg":"試下唔好睇議論文 敘事文。睇下多啲抒情、小說式，吸引到佢去睇先<br />\n入門小說：哈利波特<br />\n當年小學已經睇晒全部，係咁翻睇翻睇，所以好中意中文"},{"pid":"cf2802cc00ef050d160e3725cc6055cb55b72f6c","tid":901731,"uid":210672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:20:31.000Z","msg":"依家先中四就放棄?早左d"},{"pid":"63d04095e7e5cb1f3b7947f235ea2ecf53dd085d","tid":901731,"uid":7458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4900ec9e1df21fce149671868e4a0695a71043ad","tid":901731,"uid":33381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1484e9be4420eccaefe8d9a3e3b36b9c19d39cf2","tid":901731,"uid":7458,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:00:36.000Z","msg":"如果佢本身冇心機學中文<br />\n點幫都救唔返<br />\n<br />\n我以前都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:15:02.000Z","msg":"你而家中文都好差?<br />\n佢係差到我覺得佢上連登都好難表達自己要講咩<br />\n不過佢的確完全無心機學中文<br />\n無心機學搞到個底差 越差又越無心機學..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:21:51.000Z","msg":"係呀 好多時我想打既字好似: 認為 會變成 應為  回憶變回億<br />\n同埋好難形容我想講既野 用既詞語太簡單 (我已經咗打&quot;型容&quot; 一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) <br />\n要睇返自己寫咗乜先敢回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同佢一樣 以前努力學英文 特登唔學中文<br />\n點知而家份工係做翻譯 寫中文好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630873b492a3a6cfce5e69bf52eae4fcd08d7e79","tid":901731,"uid":33381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfb328f06e6aa1c6c851fafd2d769f1140d72b7d","tid":901731,"uid":27030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:18:21.000Z","msg":"平時講中文說話能力有冇問題先<br />\n如果冇問題應該重可以由說話開始train"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:23:57.000Z","msg":"佢算內向 唔多講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過平時同人日常溝通就應該無問題<br />\n但如果叫佢正經討論一個topic就會<br />\n邏輯錯 用字唔準確 之類...."},{"pid":"1f8cc7b26729d09b9f00ae0969228b31f96a3e77","tid":901731,"uid":33381,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ce3c1872b169716fb8cffdeeb439aad9da548d0a","tid":901731,"uid":221857,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:19:43.000Z","msg":"試下唔好睇議論文 敘事文。睇